BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tz4H2Tl6FGTayNfQLt3LA
SUMMARY:Shred-A-Thon & RX Take Back Event
DTSTAMP:20260413T004130Z
DTSTART:20260425T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Drive-Through Shred-A-Thon & Rx Take Back Event Spring cleaning
	 just got easier! Stop by our convenient drive-through event to: - Shred s
	ensitive documents - Safely dispose of unused or expired medications - Don
	ate canned goods to support local families The event is free\, quick\, and
	 easy\, and no need to leave your car! REMINDERS:  - Stay in Your Vehicle:
	 This is a drive-through event. - Prepare Your Items: Before arriving\, pl
	ace all documents and prescription drugs in your trunk\, hatchback\, or tr
	uck bed. - Limit: Up to 5 file boxes or bags of paper per vehicle. - No co
	mmercial or bulk business drop-offs allowed. \\*\\*Shredding Guidelines\\*
	\\* - Remove Metal Items: Remove paper clips and other metal items \\(stap
	les are okay\\). Not Accepted: - Plastic items such as bags\, packing mate
	rials\, credit cards\, notebooks\, DVDs\, X-rays - Previously shredded doc
	uments \\*\\*\\*RX Take Back Guidelines\\*\\*\\* Accepted Items: - Prescri
	ption and over-the-counter medications \\(pills or liquids\\). - Solid dos
	es \\(capsules\, tablets\\) can be left in the original container or place
	d in a separate bag. - If using the original container\, remove or black o
	ut personal information on the label.   NOT Accepted: - Intravenous soluti
	ons\, injectables\, needles\, inhalers\, syringes - Chemotherapy medicatio
	ns - Vaping devices with non-removable batteries - Medical waste Learn mor
	e: rentonwa.gov/shredathon\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detail
	s/shred-a-thon-rx-take-back-event/18252307/2026-04-25T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/shred-a-thon-rx-take-back
	-event/18252307/2026-04-25T00
LOCATION:Renton Stadium\, 405 Logan Ave N\, Renton\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
