SUMMARY:Earth Month Event | Restoration at Wildwood Park
DTSTAMP:20260413T004130Z
DTSTART:20260425T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Month at a Wildwood Volunteer Event!\n\nJoin  f
	or a Forest Steward led clean up  event in the Wildwood Park! Volunteers  
	will be working to remove weeds and spreading mulch. Get your hands in the
	  dirt\, work alongside neighbors and friends! No experience necessary\; g
